# Choose your Chef Automate environment

For this module you'll need a Chef Automate server. Chef Automate is a full-stack continuous automation platform which includes Chef server.

Choose where you want to manage your Chef Automate server. In the future, we'll provide options for launching Chef Automate [from the Microsoft Azure Marketplace](https://docs.chef.io/azure_portal.html#chef-automate) and [from the AWS Marketplace](https://docs.chef.io/aws_marketplace.html#chef-automate-ami).

